name: 2022 Community Poster
description:
In Spring 2022, we invited our community to sign this poster to celebrate our new [brand identity](https://gallery.mirror.xyz/1jgwdWHqYF1dUQ0YoYf-hEpd-OgJ79dZ5L00ArBQzac).

This commemorative token was made available to our users who participated in the event and were early supporters in our project.

Thank you for being a member of Gallery.
